    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wn tas KUNGS bij us\nAhbramu fazzijis: Iṣ-\neij no tawas Semmes/\nun no tawas Dsimtenes/ un no\ntawa Tehwa Namma uhs to\nSemmi/ ko es tew rahdijhu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un es darrifchu tew par\nweenu leelu Taittu/ un darrifchu\ntawu Wahrdiu leelu/ un tu buhfi\npar Swehtibu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un es fwehtifchu tohs/ kas\ntew fwehti/ un nolahdeschn to/\nkas tew nolahd/ un eeksch tewis\ntaps wiffas Senimes Ziltis fweh-\ntitas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Ahbrams aisgahje/ itt\nka tas KUNGS us to bij fazzi-\njis/ un Lats gahje ar to: Un Ah-\nbrams btja feptindefinits un pee-\nzus Gaddus wezz/ kad wiꞥſch no\nAhrana isgahje.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Ahbrams nehme Sa-\nrâi fawu Seewu/ un Lattu fawu\nBrahleuu/un wiffu winno Man-\ntu/ ko tee bij fagahdajufchi/ un\ntahs Dwebfeles/ ko tee Ahranâ\nbij dabbujuschi/ un tee isgahje/\nka tee eetu us to Semmi Rana-\nan/ un tee nahze us to Semmi\nRanân.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Ahbrams pahrftaigaja\nto Semmi/ lihds tai Weetai Si-\nkem/ lihds teemi Ohsolceim More/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad rahdijhs tas KUN\nAhbramam un fazzija: Ta\nDsimnumain dohſchn es\nSemmi/ un wiꞥſch ustaisij-\ntam KUNSAM weenu At\nkas winnam bij rahdijees.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch zehlahs no\nrenes/ ihs weenam Kalnam\ntelai prett Rihteem/ un us\nfawu Telti Betelai prett W\nra-un Ajai prett Anstruma\nun ustaisija tur tam KUNG-\nweenu Altari/ un peefai\nKUNGA Wahrdn.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Ahbrams aisgah-\ndams/ un aiseedams prett\nnas widdus Puffi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tanni Semmē\nBads/ un Ahbrams nogah-\nEgipti/ ka wiꞥſch tur u\nSwechineeks buhtu/ jo\nBads vija gruhts tanni Se-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas notikkabs/\nwiꞥſch tuwn pee Egiptes m\ntad fazzija wiꞥſch us Sar-\nwu Seewu: Raugi jelle/\nnu tew skaistu Seewu no D\neffam.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un kad tew tee Eg-\nredsehs/ fazzibs tee: Sc-\nwinnaSeewa/un nokaus m\nun paturrehs tew dsihwu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Sakki jelle/ tew ni\nMahsu effam/ ka man labb\njahs tewis deht/ un manna\nfele tewis labbad dsihwa pa\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kad nu Ahbrams E-\nSemmē nahze/ tad redseju\n"
    }
  ],
